{
  "stem": "22883.1",
  "chunk_idx": 5,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 9.5,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And probably for-- for-- for that reason she-- she thought-- she-- she said, and she said that as a compliment to my mother.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "But my mother didn't receive it as a compliment because, of course, between Polish population and Jewish population there was a big chasm, big difference and big separation.",
      "word_count": 28
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yes, of course.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yes, in every-- in every country in Europe there was a Jewish problem.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "But what-- what-- what-- what you are calling Jewish problem?",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "There were some Nazi methods or Nazi propaganda leaking from Germany to all neighboring countries.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And important, there was quite a good environment to spread such things.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I remember there was a big debate and controversy in parliament, Polish parliament, just before the war because there was-- there was one member of the parliament, a lady, [?",
      "word_count": 30
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Pristor, ?] she raised the problem of ritual slaughtering of animals.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Apparently, in Poland, all the slaughterhouses and all the people who were doing the slaughtering of animals, they were perform-- or they were doing the slaughtering according to Jewish ritual.",
      "word_count": 30
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "OK?",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "So it's so-called 'ritual slaughtering.'",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Which, you probably know, the animal was-- animal's throat was cut once, and the-- the animal had to bleed out and die.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And some animals, they were not right away-- didn't die right away, and there was some kind of suffering from side of the-- of the animals.",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Because apparently, the-- the blood has to come out from the animal before it could be recognized as kosher meat.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "This made some uproar and some controversy in the Polish population.",
      "word_count": 11
    }
  ],
